1
00:00:22,125 --> 00:00:23,750
- GOOD MORNING, YUUJI.

2
00:00:25,375 --> 00:00:26,958
IT'S BEAUTIFUL OUTSIDE TODAY.

3
00:00:27,791 --> 00:00:29,416
ARE YOU HUNGRY? HERE.

4
00:00:31,166 --> 00:00:33,500
YUUJI? YOU LOOK SLEEPY.

5
00:00:35,375 --> 00:00:36,708
- SHOUKO, TOSS ME MY CELL.

6
00:00:43,416 --> 00:00:47,625
HELLO, IS THIS THE POLICE?
I'D LIKE TO REPORT AN INTRUDER.

7
00:00:47,708 --> 00:00:49,333
( theme song playing )

8
00:02:17,791 --> 00:02:19,041
- YUUJI, WHAT IS THIS?

9
00:02:21,333 --> 00:02:25,000
- WELL, I DON'T KNOW. I'VE
NEVER SEEN THAT BOOK BEFORE.

10
00:02:25,083 --> 00:02:27,875
- REALLY? BECAUSE IT WAS HIDDEN
UNDER A FALSE BOTTOM

11
00:02:27,958 --> 00:02:29,500
IN THE THIRD DRAWER OF YOUR DESK

12
00:02:29,583 --> 00:02:32,000
WITH A SCHOOLBOOK COVER
DISGUISING IT.

13
00:02:32,083 --> 00:02:34,541
- HELLO? DID YOU HAVE
AN EMERGENCY? HELLO?

14
00:02:36,041 --> 00:02:38,333
- I'M SORRY. I MADE A MISTAKE.

15
00:02:39,833 --> 00:02:42,000
- ALL RIGHT, IF YOU BURN IT,
I WILL FORGIVE YOU.

16
00:02:42,083 --> 00:02:44,583
- WHY WOULD I DO THAT? WHAT
DO I CARE IF YOU FORGIVE ME?

17
00:02:44,666 --> 00:02:47,000
- FINE. I'LL TAKE CARE
OF IT MYSELF.

18
00:02:47,083 --> 00:02:48,666
- YOU CAN'T JUST TORCH
SOMEONE'S STUFF!

19
00:02:50,708 --> 00:02:53,458
( Yuuji screams )

20
00:02:53,541 --> 00:02:55,541
SO TELL ME WHAT ARE YOU DOING
HERE ANYWAY?

21
00:02:56,916 --> 00:02:58,166
- LET ME SHOW YOU.

22
00:02:59,458 --> 00:03:01,875
- WAIT. THE VIP TICKET
FOR THE AMUSEMENT PARK?

23
00:03:01,958 --> 00:03:03,500
HOW DID YOU GET THAT?

24
00:03:03,583 --> 00:03:06,000
- SOMEONE GENEROUS
GAVE IT TO ME.

25
00:03:06,083 --> 00:03:07,750
- YEAH, RIGHT, SOMEONE GENEROUS.

26
00:03:07,833 --> 00:03:09,458
AKIHISA WAS THE ONE
WHO ENDED UP WITH THOSE TICKETS.

27
00:03:09,541 --> 00:03:12,000
- Akihisa: WASN'T ME.
I'M NOT GUILTY!

28
00:03:12,083 --> 00:03:14,166
- WE HAVE SPECIAL PASSES
TO THE WEDDING EXPERIENCE.

29
00:03:15,333 --> 00:03:16,291
( phone ringing )

30
00:03:17,916 --> 00:03:19,500
- Akihisa: HELLO?
WHO MAY I ASK IS CALLING?

31
00:03:19,583 --> 00:03:21,166
- ( in menacing tone )
I'M GONNA KILL YOU!

32
00:03:21,250 --> 00:03:23,666
- WHAT? BUT WHY?
WHO ARE YOU? PLEASE DON'T.

33
00:03:23,750 --> 00:03:26,416
- WELL. IT'S TIME. LET'S GO.
- NO WAY.

34
00:03:26,500 --> 00:03:27,708
- SO YOU LIED TO ME?

35
00:03:27,791 --> 00:03:29,583
- I HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

36
00:03:29,666 --> 00:03:31,541
- YOU PROMISED THAT
YOU WOULD GO OUT WITH ME

37
00:03:31,625 --> 00:03:33,708
BACK WHEN YOU LOST THE ST WAR.

38
00:03:33,791 --> 00:03:36,625
- I DON'T REMEMBER THAT AT ALL.
- IT'S YOUR CHOICE.

39
00:03:36,708 --> 00:03:38,250
YOU SWORE IF YOU
BROKE YOUR PROMISE,

40
00:03:38,333 --> 00:03:40,000
YOU WOULD MARRY ME RIGHT AWAY.

41
00:03:40,083 --> 00:03:42,583
- OKAY, NOW YOU'RE JUST
MAKING THINGS UP.

42
00:03:42,666 --> 00:03:44,166
- ( firecrackers exploding )

43
00:03:45,916 --> 00:03:47,458
- OF COURSE. THIS IS
ALL AKIHISA'S FAULT.

44
00:03:47,541 --> 00:03:48,166
I'M GONNA KILL HIM.

45
00:03:48,250 --> 00:03:50,583
ARGH! WOULD YOU LET GO?

46
00:03:50,666 --> 00:03:52,000
HOW COME EVERY TIME YOU TOUCH ME
IT HAS TO HURT?

47
00:03:52,083 --> 00:03:53,125
- COUPLES ARE SUPPOSED TO WALK
ARM IN ARM LIKE THIS.

48
00:03:53,208 --> 00:03:54,625
- REALLY?

49
00:03:54,708 --> 00:03:57,666
BECAUSE I DON'T SEE ANY OTHER
CHICKS USING BRUTE FORCE!

50
00:03:57,750 --> 00:04:01,750
- HELLO, LOVERS! WE'D LIKE TO
GIVE YOU A BIG FAT WELCOME!

51
00:04:05,833 --> 00:04:07,000
( phone ringing )

52
00:04:07,083 --> 00:04:08,791
HELLO?

53
00:04:08,875 --> 00:04:10,916
- HEY, YOU JERK WAD, I BET YOU
GUYS THINK YOU'RE REALLY FUNNY,

54
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:13,000
DON'T YOU?

55
00:04:13,083 --> 00:04:15,750
- RUN! I'M INNOCENT!

56
00:04:15,833 --> 00:04:17,791
- IF THAT'S TRUE, THEN WHY
THE HELL ARE YOU RUNNING?

57
00:04:21,666 --> 00:04:24,666
I CAN'T BELIEVE YOU'RE A PART OF
THIS WHOLE THING TOO, HIDEYOSHI!

58
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:30,125
- WHO DID YOU SAY? I HAPPEN TO
BE A MEMBER OF THE STAFF HERE.

59
00:04:30,208 --> 00:04:33,583
THIS IS MY OCCUPATION. I AM NOT
ACQUAINTED WITH THIS PERSON

60
00:04:33,666 --> 00:04:35,375
TO WHOM YOU ARE REFERRING.

61
00:04:35,458 --> 00:04:37,458
- REALLY? I'M SUPPOSED
TO BELIEVE THAT?

62
00:04:38,250 --> 00:04:39,208
( phone ringing )

63
00:04:41,083 --> 00:04:43,500
- OH HEAVENS, MY HAND
JUST SLIPPED FOR NO REASON.

64
00:04:43,583 --> 00:04:44,666
- OF COURSE IT DID.

65
00:04:46,208 --> 00:04:47,875
- MAY I PLEASE HAVE
YOUR TICKETS NOW, FOLKS?

66
00:04:48,666 --> 00:04:50,166
- HERE.

67
00:04:50,250 --> 00:04:53,625
- WHOA! WOULD YOU LOOK AT THAT.
YOU HAVE VIP PASSES WITH YOU!

68
00:04:53,708 --> 00:04:55,833
ALPHA CALLING BRAVO.
I'VE CONFIRMED THE TARGET.

69
00:04:55,916 --> 00:04:58,625
WE HAVE A CODE SEVEN AND ARE
SHIFTING TO OPERATION WEDDING.

70
00:04:58,708 --> 00:05:00,250
REPEAT: OPERATION WEDDING.

71
00:05:00,333 --> 00:05:03,166
- WE'RE STANDING RIGHT HERE.
IT'S NOT LIKE WE CAN'T HEAR YOU!

72
00:05:03,250 --> 00:05:05,583
- PLEASE CALM DOWN, SIR.
IT'S NOT YOUR CONCERN.

73
00:05:05,666 --> 00:05:07,583
- YOU WERE JUST
TALKING ABOUT ME!

74
00:05:07,666 --> 00:05:09,000
- NOW THEN,

75
00:05:09,083 --> 00:05:11,666
IT'S ABOUT TIME FOR US TO TAKE A
COMPLIMENTARY PICTURE.

76
00:05:14,041 --> 00:05:15,041
- SMILE.

77
00:05:16,666 --> 00:05:18,333
- SHOUKO, SORRY!

78
00:05:20,666 --> 00:05:22,125
AM I SUPPOSED TO NOT NOTICE

79
00:05:22,208 --> 00:05:25,166
IT'S YOU DOWN THERE BEING YOUR
PERVERTED SELF?

80
00:05:25,250 --> 00:05:26,208
HEH!

81
00:05:27,625 --> 00:05:30,541
- YUUJI, BE NICE.

82
00:05:30,625 --> 00:05:32,166
- OKAY, I'LL DO MY BEST.

83
00:05:32,250 --> 00:05:34,291
- GOOD. I'LL REWARD YOU LATER.

84
00:05:34,375 --> 00:05:36,500
- NO! HOW MANY TIMES
DO I HAVE TO TELL YOU,

85
00:05:36,583 --> 00:05:38,583
I DON'T GIVE A CRAP
WHAT YOUR UNDERWEAR LOOKS LIKE.

86
00:05:40,375 --> 00:05:42,333
- Shouko: I WILL NEVER
FORGIVE YOU FOR THAT.

87
00:05:42,416 --> 00:05:44,708
- STOP IT! PUSHING DOWN ON
SOMEONE'S TEMPLES LIKE THAT

88
00:05:44,791 --> 00:05:45,791
CAN CAUSE BRAIN DAMAGE!

89
00:05:45,875 --> 00:05:48,041
- CHEESE!
- Shouko: CHEESE.

90
00:05:52,208 --> 00:05:53,583
- Yuuji: WHAT THE HELL
IS THIS PICTURE?

91
00:05:53,666 --> 00:05:55,583
- IT'S A FREE SOUVENIR
FOR THE HAPPY COUPLE.

92
00:05:55,666 --> 00:05:57,416
- IT'LL BE PUT UP IN
THE PARK'S PHOTO STUDIO

93
00:05:57,500 --> 00:05:59,250
SO EVERYONE CAN SEE IT!

94
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:01,416
- YOU CAN'T DO THAT!

95
00:06:01,500 --> 00:06:03,291
- YUUJI, DON'T BE SHY.

96
00:06:03,375 --> 00:06:05,750
- I'M NOT BEING SHY. I JUST
DON'T WANT THIS PICTURE UP.

97
00:06:05,833 --> 00:06:08,250
- COOL! CHECK IT OUT, BABY!

98
00:06:08,333 --> 00:06:10,625
LET'S HAVE THEM TAKE
OUR PICTURE, TOO!

99
00:06:10,708 --> 00:06:13,583
- WHATEVER YOU WANT, SUGAR.
HEY, LITTLE DUDE!

100
00:06:13,666 --> 00:06:15,375
YOU CAN GO AHEAD
AND TAKE OUR PICTURE NEXT.

101
00:06:15,458 --> 00:06:18,875
- UNFORTUNATELY, GOOD SIR,
THIS SERVICE IS ONLY AVAILABLE

102
00:06:18,958 --> 00:06:20,791
TO OUR VIP TICKET HOLDERS.

103
00:06:20,875 --> 00:06:24,208
- WHAT? WE'RE CUSTOMERS, TOO,
AND JUST ASKING FOR ONE PICTURE,

104
00:06:24,291 --> 00:06:26,375
SO WHAT'S THE BIG DEAL?

105
00:06:26,458 --> 00:06:28,541
WOULDN'T YOU RATHER HAVE
A HOT COUPLE ON DISPLAY

106
00:06:28,625 --> 00:06:32,583
INSTEAD OF
THOSE LAME TWEENIES. WELL?

107
00:06:32,666 --> 00:06:35,916
- IT'S TRUE. I MEAN, LOOK AT US.
IT'S NOT LIKE HIGH SCHOOL KIDS

108
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:37,458
CAN COMPARE, RIGHT?

109
00:06:38,666 --> 00:06:41,250
- HOLD ON.
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

110
00:06:41,333 --> 00:06:43,958
- I WILL NOT ALLOW THEM
TO TALK THAT WAY ABOUT US.

111
00:06:44,041 --> 00:06:46,375
- DON'T LET THOSE JERKS
GET TO YOU, OKAY?

112
00:06:46,458 --> 00:06:48,375
- ALL RIGHT THEN,
IF THAT'S WHAT YOU WANT.

113
00:06:48,458 --> 00:06:50,583
- WE WANT TO HAVE A PICTURE
JUST LIKE THEY HAD!

114
00:06:50,666 --> 00:06:53,125
- ALL RIGHT. IF YOU INSIST,
WE'LL DO IT.

115
00:06:53,208 --> 00:06:54,416
PLEASE COME THIS WAY.

116
00:06:55,666 --> 00:06:57,791
IF YOU COULD PUT YOUR HAND
RIGHT HERE.

117
00:06:57,875 --> 00:06:59,541
NOW, SQUEEZE AS HARD AS YOU CAN.

118
00:06:59,625 --> 00:07:01,416
- ( man groans )

119
00:07:01,500 --> 00:07:02,833
- CHEESE.
- Girl: CHEESE.

120
00:07:04,208 --> 00:07:05,750
- WHAT THE HELL
DO YOU THINK YOU'RE DOING?

121
00:07:05,833 --> 00:07:07,583
- SAID YOU WANTED US
TO TAKE THE SAME PICTURE.

122
00:07:07,666 --> 00:07:10,583
- I HOPE YOU RUN FAST,
'CAUSE I'M GONNA KILL YOU!

123
00:07:10,666 --> 00:07:12,166
- GO-GO! BURGER HEAD'S
LOST HIS MIND!

124
00:07:12,250 --> 00:07:13,916
- ARE YOU MAKING FUN OF ME,
YOU PUNK?

125
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,500
- WOULD YOU LIKE FRIES
WITH THAT, SIR?

126
00:07:15,583 --> 00:07:18,833
- OF COURSE. YOU KNOW, IF
YOU WANTED TO LEAVE INTSEAD,

127
00:07:18,916 --> 00:07:25,333
I'D BE COOL WITH IT.

128
00:07:25,416 --> 00:07:26,708
DOESN'T IT BOTHER YOU AT ALL

129
00:07:26,791 --> 00:07:29,333
THAT EVERYONE CAN SEE
WHAT YOU'RE DOING TO ME?

130
00:07:29,416 --> 00:07:31,041
- DON'T BE SHY. RELAX.

131
00:07:31,125 --> 00:07:34,333
- I'M NOT BEING SHY, I JUST
PREFER NOT BE HURTING!

132
00:07:34,416 --> 00:07:36,291
- BUT THIS IS HOW COUPLES WALK.

133
00:07:36,375 --> 00:07:38,583
- IT'S ARM IN ARM,
NOT ARM IN PAIN!

134
00:07:38,666 --> 00:07:41,666
- GREETINGS TO THE ADORABLE
LOOKING COUPLE OVER THERE!

135
00:07:43,666 --> 00:07:45,583
- SEE. I TOLD YOU
WE LOOKED LIKE A COUPLE.

136
00:07:45,666 --> 00:07:47,583
- SHE'S A GIANT FUZZ BALL.
WHAT DOES SHE KNOW?

137
00:07:47,666 --> 00:07:49,166
- I AM FEE THE FOX.

138
00:07:49,250 --> 00:07:52,333
PLEASE ALLOW ME TO SHOW YOU A
FUN AND INTERESTING ATTRACTION.

139
00:07:52,416 --> 00:07:54,916
- EARLIER I COULD'VE SWORN
AKIHISA WAS OUT

140
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,583
ON A DATE WITH SOME CHICK.

141
00:07:56,666 --> 00:08:00,458
- WHAT? YOU SAW YOSHII?
WHERE IS HE? WHERE DID THEY GO?

142
00:08:00,541 --> 00:08:01,708
- HELLO, THERE, HIMEJI.

143
00:08:04,166 --> 00:08:05,541
- ( train whistle toots )

144
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:09,500
- I AM FEE THE FOX.

145
00:08:09,583 --> 00:08:12,583
PLEASE ALLOW ME TO SHOW YOU A
FUN AND INTERESTING ATTRACTION.

146
00:08:12,666 --> 00:08:14,791
- LOOK, IF YOU WANT TO PLAY
INNOCENT, THAT'S FINE.

147
00:08:14,875 --> 00:08:18,041
WHY DON'T YOU JUST TELL US WHERE
WE SHOULD GO THEN, ALL RIGHT?

148
00:08:18,125 --> 00:08:21,333
OKAY! DON'T MISS THE HAUNTED
HOUSE RIGHT OVER THERE!

149
00:08:21,416 --> 00:08:22,916
YOU SHOULD GO NOW!

150
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:26,041
- AWESOME. SHOUKO, WE'RE GOING
ANYWHERE BUT THAT HAUNTED HOUSE.

151
00:08:26,125 --> 00:08:29,958
- WAIT! YOU HAVE TO GO!
WHY DON'T YOU WANNA?

152
00:08:30,041 --> 00:08:32,583
- BECAUSE I'M SURE YOU GUYS HAVE
SET UP SOMETHING STUPID THERE.

153
00:08:32,666 --> 00:08:35,041
- PLEASE! GO TO
THE HAUNTED HOUSE!

154
00:08:35,125 --> 00:08:37,541
YOU DON'T WANT TO MISS OUT
ON IT! PLEASE!

155
00:08:38,583 --> 00:08:39,750
- NOT HAPPENING.

156
00:08:39,833 --> 00:08:41,375
- STOP RIGHT THERE, YUUJI!

157
00:08:41,458 --> 00:08:44,583
I'M NOIN, AND I WILL NOT
LET YOU MAKE FEE CRY ANYMORE!

158
00:08:44,666 --> 00:08:47,916
- OH, COME ON, YOUR HEAD'S
ALL MESSED UP, AKIHISA.

159
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:50,583
- HOW RUDE!
WHICH PART IS MESSED UP?

160
00:08:50,666 --> 00:08:53,583
- YUUJI, NOIN IS
THE ABSENTMINDED ONE.

161
00:08:53,666 --> 00:08:54,916
- I DON'T CARE.

162
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:56,958
WHAT KINDA FOX WOULD HAVE
HIS HEAD ON BACKWARDS?

163
00:08:57,041 --> 00:08:59,583
- YOSHII! YOU PUT YOUR HEAD ON
THE WRONG WAY!

164
00:08:59,666 --> 00:09:02,000
- WHAT? DAMN IT! NO WONDER
I COULDN'T SEE ANYTHING.

165
00:09:02,083 --> 00:09:04,375
- HURRY AND FIX IT BEFORE THEY
FIGURE OUT WHO WE ARE!

166
00:09:04,458 --> 00:09:06,000
- Akihisa: WHAT'S HAPPENING?
WHERE AM I?

167
00:09:06,083 --> 00:09:08,333
- THE SAD THING IS, THEY REALLY
THINK THEY'VE FOOLED US.

168
00:09:09,666 --> 00:09:11,250
- OH, BY THE WAY,

169
00:09:11,333 --> 00:09:13,916
HOW DID YOUR DATE WITH THAT
SUPER HOT COLLEGE CHICK GO, MAN?

170
00:09:14,666 --> 00:09:15,708
- WHAT?

171
00:09:17,666 --> 00:09:20,791
- YOSHII, I HEARD
WHILE WE WERE WORKING

172
00:09:20,875 --> 00:09:22,458
ON THIS VERY
IMPORTANT ASSIGNMENT

173
00:09:22,541 --> 00:09:24,583
THAT YOU WENT OUT ON A DATE.

174
00:09:24,666 --> 00:09:27,583
- WAIT. WHERE'D YOU HEAR THAT?

175
00:09:27,666 --> 00:09:30,000
- MINAMI'S ON HER WAY
HERE NOW.

176
00:09:30,083 --> 00:09:32,583
WE THINK WE NEED TO SIT DOWN
AND TALK ABOUT IT.

177
00:09:32,666 --> 00:09:35,500
- NO! BAD IDEA. THIS PARK IS
SUPPOSED TO BE FOR AMUSEMENT

178
00:09:35,583 --> 00:09:36,708
NOT A-FIGHTING!

179
00:09:36,791 --> 00:09:39,583
- HEY! WHAT THE HELL
IS GOING ON HERE, AKI?

180
00:09:39,666 --> 00:09:42,208
- HOW'D SHE GET HERE SO FAST?

181
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:46,583
TRASH CAN! AND GROUND!

182
00:09:46,666 --> 00:09:48,416
- YOU'RE GONNA TELL US
EVERY SINGLE DETAIL.

183
00:09:48,500 --> 00:09:50,583
- AND YOU NEED TO TELL US
THE TRUTH, TOO.

184
00:09:50,666 --> 00:09:53,291
- I DON'T KNOW WHAT'S GOING ON.

185
00:09:53,375 --> 00:09:54,625
- LET'S GET OUT OF HERE, SHOUKO.

186
00:09:54,708 --> 00:09:56,041
WHAT DO YOU SAY WE GO RIDE
THE FERRIS WHEEL

187
00:09:56,125 --> 00:09:57,416
OR SOMETHING LIKE THAT?

188
00:09:57,500 --> 00:09:58,875
SHOUKO? WHERE'D YOU...

189
00:10:00,041 --> 00:10:01,291
- ( dramatic music playing )

190
00:10:01,375 --> 00:10:03,125
- EVERYTHING SET UP,
THE HAUNTED HOUSE IS READY.

191
00:10:06,291 --> 00:10:08,791
- STOP THAT!
- WE'RE GOING WHERE THEY WANT.

192
00:10:08,875 --> 00:10:11,458
- AH, WHAT THE HELL
DID HIDEYOSHI SAY TO YOU?

193
00:10:11,541 --> 00:10:13,791
- THAT I CAN JUMP INTO
YOUR ARMS IN THERE.

194
00:10:17,625 --> 00:10:19,875
- SIGN THIS BEFORE ENTERING.
- SIGN WHAT?

195
00:10:19,958 --> 00:10:22,958
- LIABILITY WAIVER.
SUCH WAIVERS ARE OFTEN PREPARED

196
00:10:23,041 --> 00:10:26,583
IN THESE TYPES OF DANGEROUS
SITUATIONS. JUST IN CASE.

197
00:10:26,666 --> 00:10:29,916
- REALLY? SO THIS PLACE IS
ACTUALLY DANGEROUS?

198
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:31,583
AT LEAST THAT'LL
MAKE IT INTERESTING.

199
00:10:31,666 --> 00:10:35,250
WHAT'S IT SAY?
WAIVER: I, YUUJI SAKAMOTO,

200
00:10:35,333 --> 00:10:37,375
WILL LOVE SHOUKO KIRISHIMA
AS MY WIFE

201
00:10:37,458 --> 00:10:40,166
AS LONG AS I LIVE AND WILL SHARE
MY JOYS AND SORROWS WITH HER.

202
00:10:40,250 --> 00:10:42,000
SO I SWEAR?

203
00:10:42,083 --> 00:10:44,500
- HERE'S A PEN.
- AND A REGISTERED SEAL.

204
00:10:44,583 --> 00:10:45,750
- INK PAD TO STAMP IT WITH.

205
00:10:45,833 --> 00:10:47,625
- WHAT THE HELL?
AM I THE ONLY ONE

206
00:10:47,708 --> 00:10:49,583
WHO FINDS THIS
ENTIRE THING RIDICULOUS?

207
00:10:49,666 --> 00:10:51,875
- UNDER THE CARBON SHEET
IS A SECOND SHEET,

208
00:10:51,958 --> 00:10:53,583
YOUR MARRIAGE REGISTRATION FORM.

209
00:10:53,666 --> 00:10:55,833
- HOW CONSIDERATE.
- NO, IT ISN'T!

210
00:11:01,041 --> 00:11:02,750
- Shouko: BAKA AND TEST.

211
00:11:05,291 --> 00:11:06,583
- PLEASE, COME THIS WAY.

212
00:11:06,666 --> 00:11:09,125
- WOULD YOU MIND
HOLDING MY BAG FOR ME?

213
00:11:09,208 --> 00:11:11,000
- MAKE SURE WHAT'S INSIDE
DOESN'T FALL OUT.

214
00:11:11,083 --> 00:11:13,833
- AS YOU WISH.

215
00:11:13,916 --> 00:11:15,875
WELL THEN, I HOPE YOU ENJOY
YOURSELVES

216
00:11:15,958 --> 00:11:18,041
WHILST BEING
THOROUGHLY TERRIFIED.

