- SHOUKO, THERE'S SOMETHING
I REALLY NEED TO SAY.

437
00:21:02,750 --> 00:21:04,708
YOU SHOULDN'T FEEL THE WAY
THAT YOU DO ABOUT ME.

438
00:21:04,791 --> 00:21:06,833
IT'S A BIG MISTAKE.

439
00:21:06,916 --> 00:21:09,250
SEVEN YEARS AGO, I WAS STUPID.

440
00:21:09,333 --> 00:21:11,375
AND YOU GOT SUCKED INTO
ALL THAT.

441
00:21:11,458 --> 00:21:14,125
I WAS ONLY EVER TRYING TO TAKE
RESPONSIBILITY, THAT'S ALL.

442
00:21:14,208 --> 00:21:16,208
NOTHING ELSE.

443
00:21:16,291 --> 00:21:18,750
ALL THIS TIME YOU'VE BEEN
WASTING YOUR DREAMS ON ME.

444
00:21:18,833 --> 00:21:20,583
AND I KNOW I'M NOT WORTH IT.

445
00:21:21,375 --> 00:21:22,416
- ( Shouko whimpers )

446
00:21:23,708 --> 00:21:25,750
- BELIEVE ME. I'M REALLY SORRY.

447
00:21:25,833 --> 00:21:27,833
- YUUJI, I...

448
00:21:27,916 --> 00:21:30,541
- LISTEN TO ME. YOUR DREAM
IS NOTHING TO LAUGH AT!

449
00:21:33,291 --> 00:21:36,083
YEAH, YOU MAY HAVE PICKED
THE WRONG GUY,

450
00:21:36,166 --> 00:21:38,250
BUT I THINK CARING ABOUT SOMEONE
FOR SUCH A LONG TIME

451
00:21:38,333 --> 00:21:40,250
IS A WONDERFUL THING.

452
00:21:40,333 --> 00:21:43,250
WHAT YOU WANT IS AMAZING,
AND YOU SHOULD BE PROUD OF IT.

453
00:21:43,333 --> 00:21:45,166
THAT'S WHAT MAKES YOU
SO SPECIAL.

454
00:21:45,250 --> 00:21:48,541
ALTHOUGH, YOU PROBABLY WANT TO
GO WITH THE RIGHT MAN NEXT TIME.

455
00:21:50,291 --> 00:21:52,750
IT MIGHT WORK OUT BETTER.
( chuckles )

456
00:21:52,833 --> 00:21:55,750
WELL, THEN, GUESS IT'S NOT EVERY
DAY YOU ALMOST GET MARRIED.

457
00:21:55,833 --> 00:21:58,208
YOU MIGHT AS WELL HAVE SOME KIND
OF SOUVENIR FROM IT, RIGHT?

458
00:21:58,291 --> 00:21:59,666
- BUT, YUUJI, WAIT.

459
00:21:59,750 --> 00:22:03,041
- OH, YEAH! I ALMOST FORGOT.

460
00:22:03,125 --> 00:22:04,916
THANKS FOR THAT
LUNCH YOU MADE.

461
00:22:05,000 --> 00:22:08,041
IT WAS DELICIOUS.

462
00:22:08,125 --> 00:22:09,541
LET'S GO HOME.

463
00:22:09,625 --> 00:22:11,833
IF IT GETS ANY LATER, PEOPLE
WILL THINK WE'RE TOGETHER.

464
00:22:11,916 --> 00:22:12,958
- YUUJI!

465
00:22:13,750 --> 00:22:15,250
- WHAT NOW?

466
00:22:15,333 --> 00:22:19,291
- I KNEW IT. I KNEW THERE WAS NO
WAY I COULD BE WRONG ABOUT YOU!

467
00:22:21,250 --> 00:22:22,708
- ( theme song playing )

